{"id": "ehl1665703279524", "title": "Warning: No SQL could be generated for <Entity.Model>, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path <$Path> to TCP, and the remote installation failed to connect to the requested database driver.", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Messages Reference", "SQL Generation Messages", "Warning: No SQL could be generated for <Entity.Model>, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path <$Path> to TCP, and the remote installation failed to connect to the requested database driver."], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ehl1665703279524.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Warning: No SQL could be generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path &lt;$Path&gt; to TCP, and the remote installation failed to connect to the requested database driver.</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: Warning: No SQL could be generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path &lt;$Path&gt; to a different DBMS driver  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: Warning: No SQL could be generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path &lt;$Path&gt; to a different DBMS driver  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scb1665703279442.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option &lt;Option&gt; as specified in the assignment file, [DRIVER_SE